data.text:
Visit

General admission can be reserved in advance and is always FREE for residents of Wayne, Oakland, and Macomb counties.

Collection

Browse our vast collection online and learn more about the art and its conservation.

Events & Exhibitions

Discover what's happening at your DIA and what the DIA is doing in your community.

Learning

Bring the DIA to your home or classroom with resources for students, teachers, families and everyone.

Community

Did you know DIA is free for everyone living in Macomb, Oakland, and Wayne counties? Learn more about how we impact our community inside and outside of our walls.
